PHPCompatibility  (verification only)
  Licence: LGPL-3.0
  Source:  https://github.com/PHPCompatibility/PHPCompatibility
  Pinned:  develop commit d9a91bdf66d39fbd5c22272a592c8b63a1d0954f
  Used for: cross-checking the cache-derived versions only. NewFunctionsSniff
            verifies added; RemovedFunctionsSniff verifies removed (its true
